               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17880227-81-cd403" type="crimeDate">13th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-81-off402 t17880227-81-cd403"></join>, a silver tea-spoon, value 2 s.
            </rs> the propertie of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880227-81-victim805" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Barrie
                  <interp inst="t17880227-81-victim805" type="surname" value="Barrie"></interp>
